{"tid":624890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線女記者直播遭兩外籍男強吻 平機會指或涉性騷擾","createTime":"2018-04-11T04:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T15:16:47.000Z","uid":58335,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"33eebd702589771c81e9e91301829fb9210225df","tid":624890,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"FB留言D女人唔見晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返小貓三,四隻,講D咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLala Pikka Lau 大家說話可否不要那麼嘴賤？追究又被一些人說小題大作，不追究又被人說是崇洋。你設身處地站在她的位置，被人這樣說你會好過嗎？<br />\n大家放過當時人，積下陰德好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞台女記者郭海𣿭周日在香港國際七人欖球賽決賽期間，被兩名外籍男觀眾同時強吻面頰。郭海𣿭事後接受傳媒訪問時表示無奈及不能接受，但「覺得唔可以點」。平機會回應傳媒查詢表示，此行為可能涉及性騷擾，但是否在《性別歧視條例》涵蓋範圍內，亦需視乎實際情況及雙方關係，籲當事人如有需要可與平機會聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n香港國際七人欖球賽上周五至周日舉行。由有線新聞片段所見，郭海𣿭當時在觀眾席內做直播，身後兩名外籍男觀眾在互打眼色後，一同親吻郭兩邊面頰，郭馬上推開兩人並繼續進行直播。郭事後在其個人facebook上載有關片段並表示當時身心極度疲憊故表現冷靜。有線電視新聞執行董事趙應春早前曾指有線並不打算追究，並稱「一笑置之」，日前再回應指記者若有需要公司會配合，但現階段該女記者並無提任何需要。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180411/58058725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58058725&d=rl0hN6gtZXEZsXlO8Z7T2y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ffb3a802\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58058725&h=32d78402\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180411/58058725</a>"},{"pid":"aa7634885ecf7bc27340058141a31c699c652156","tid":624890,"uid":6644,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:15:46.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要，女權撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb833eaf797b2b17dc128e0a4ebc3f3b35a32b65","tid":624890,"uid":58335,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"aa7634885ecf7bc27340058141a31c699c652156","tid":624890,"uid":6644,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:15:46.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要，女權撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:17:32.000Z","msg":"你試下調返轉係港男錫<br />\n<br />\nD女人仲唔嘈到拆天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12ce9369d35e9dff9a230da48499906972b9448","tid":624890,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32f5780947aa55bee3dafce0d1ed2470a3f6ce47","tid":624890,"uid":55488,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83aea96b1a995ac51336519559beddc41105b1e2","tid":624890,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:30:05.000Z","msg":"d鬼佬飲左兩杯啤酒就藉機抽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193a757a1ffb1e9d09588c58ff3761a227ba7318","tid":624890,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d12ce9369d35e9dff9a230da48499906972b9448","tid":624890,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:31:21.000Z","msg":"我想俾你嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60166e6a09affbac6a77fd945c1e998b8651d408","tid":624890,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0fb60934f00325f09e1db6e67659cc26144d657","tid